quran[25{c,v,t}:
78,31,yaqeenan Muttaqiyun ke liye kaamrani ka aik maqam hai
78,32,baagh aur angoor
78,33,aur no khaiz hum sun larkiyan
78,34,aur chalakte hue jaam
78,35,wahan koi laghu aur jhooti baat woh nah sunen ge
78,36,jaza aur kaafi inaam tumahray Rab ki taraf se
78,37,uss nihayat meharban khuda ki taraf se jo zameen aur asmano ka aur un ke darmain ki har cheez ka maalik hai jis ke samnay kisi ko bolnay ka yaara nahi
78,38,"jis roz rooh aur mulaika saf basta kharray hunge, koi nah bolay ga siwaye uss ke jisay rehman ijazat day aur jo theek baat kahe"
78,39,"woh din barhaq hai, ab jis ka jee chahay apne Rab ki taraf palatnay ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le"
78,40,"hum ne tum logon ko uss azaab se dara diya hai jo qareeb aa laga hai jis roz aadmi woh sab kuch dekh le ga jo is ke hathon ne agay bheja hai, aur kafir pukaar utthay ga ke kash mein khaak hota"
79,1,qasam hai unn ( firshton ki ) jo doob kar khinchte hain
79,2,aur ahistagi se nikaal le jatay hain
79,3,aur ( unn firshton ki jo kaayenaat mein ) taizi se tairtay phirtay hain
79,4,phir ( hukum baja laane mein ) Sabqat karte hain
79,5,phir ( ehkaam Ellahi ke mutabiq ) mamlaat ka intizam chillate hain
79,6,jis roz hila maaray ga zalzalay ka jhatka
79,7,aur is ke peechay aik aur jhatka parre ga
79,8,kuch dil hon ge jo uss roz khauf se kanp rahay hon ge
79,9,nigehain unn ki sehmi hui hon gi
79,10,"yeh log kehte hain"" kya waqai hum palta kar phir wapas laaye jayen ge ?"
79,11,"kya jab hum khokhli boseedah haddiyan ban chuke hon ge? """
79,12,"kehnay lagey"" yeh wapsi to phir barray ghatay ki hogi! """
79,13,halaank yeh bas itna kaam hai ke aik zor ki daant parre gi
79,14,aur yakayak yeh khulay maidan mein mojood hon ge
79,15,kya tumhe moose ke qissay ki khabar pohanchi hai ?
